---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<style>
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; }
    to { opacity: 1; }
  }

  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-out;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .hero p {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .intro {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-out 0.2s both;
  }

  .intro p {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .intro strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .tools-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .tool-card {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem 1.75rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--color-text);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease-out forwards;
  }

  .tool-card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
  .tool-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .tool-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
  .tool-card:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
  .tool-card:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }

  .tool-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.02);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .tool-card .icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .tool-card .icon svg {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    stroke: var(--color-accent);
    fill: none;
    stroke-width: 1.8;
    stroke-linecap: round;
    stroke-linejoin: round;
  }

  .tool-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
  }

  .tool-card p {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .tool-card .tag {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    background: rgba(74, 103, 65, 0.08);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .tools-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
    }
  }
</style>

<BaseLayout title="NYTools">
  <section>
    <div class="hero">
      <h1>NYTools</h1>
      <p>一套基於 P2P 技術的即時工具集，免安裝、免登入、開網頁就能用</p>
    </div>

    <div class="intro">
      <p>所有工具皆採用 <strong>WebRTC</strong> 與 <strong>PeerJS</strong> 實現，完全無伺服器架構。資料在瀏覽器之間點對點直接傳送，確保隱私與即時性。只需一個 GitHub Pages 連結即可運行。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="tools-grid">
      <a href="/Diary/nytools/chat" class="tool-card">
        <div class="icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>NY CHAT</h3>
        <p>P2P 分散式客服排隊系統。客人自動掃描所有空閒櫃台，任一櫃台空出即瞬間接通。支援多客服同時在線，WebRTC 點對點加密傳輸。</p>
        <span class="tag">WebRTC</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/Diary/nytools/drop" class="tool-card">
        <div class="icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M21.44 11.05l-9.19 9.19a6 6 0 0 1-8.49-8.49l9.19-9.19a4 4 0 0 1 5.66 5.66l-9.2 9.19a2 2 0 0 1-2.83-2.83l8.49-8.48" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>NY DROP</h3>
        <p>P2P 檔案傳輸工具。透過 6 位數代碼快速配對，檔案直接從 A 電腦傳送到 B 電腦，無伺服器儲存、無容量限制，隱私安全滿分。</p>
        <span class="tag">P2P Transfer</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/Diary/nytools/piano" class="tool-card">
        <div class="icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M9 18V5l12-2v13" />
            <circle cx="6" cy="18" r="3" />
            <circle cx="18" cy="16" r="3" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>NYPIANO</h3>
        <p>即時點播小工具。聽眾透過 P2P 連線點歌，演奏者即時收到所有點歌請求。同步顯示歌單與演奏狀態，純前端部署。</p>
        <span class="tag">Real-time</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/Diary/nytools/screen" class="tool-card">
        <div class="icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2" />
            <line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21" />
            <line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>NY Screen</h3>
        <p>投影神器。免安裝、免登入、免配對碼，開網頁就能投影。支援全螢幕顯示，使用 PeerJS + STUN/TURN 跨網段連線。</p>
        <span class="tag">Screen Share</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/Diary/nytools/clock" class="tool-card">
        <div class="icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" />
            <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>FocusClock</h3>
        <p>精美計時器工具。支援多組計時器同時運行、環形進度條、自訂鈴聲、暫停/繼續，介面仿 macOS 風格，純前端運行。</p>
        <span class="tag">Timer</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
